cmp: Subtracts {instr.right} from {instr.left} and discards the result, but sets the CPU flags accordingly.
test: Takes the logical and of {instr.right} and {instr.left} and discards the result, but sets the CPU flags accordingly.
cpuid: Writes processor identification information into eax, ebx, ecx, and edx
xgetbv: Reads the contents of the extended control register (xcr) specified in the ecx register into registers edx:eax
rdtsc: Loads the current value of the processor's time-stamp counter into registers edx:eax
